name: cloudresumechallenge
description: This repository will be used to maintain my CRC work.  1. Certification Your resume needs to have the AWS Cloud Practitioner certification on it. This is an introductory certification that orients you on the industry-leading AWS cloud – if you have a more advanced AWS cert, that’s fine but not expected. You can sit this exam online for $100 USD. A Cloud Guru offers exam prep resources.
